{
  "stem": "8703.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he learned a lesson, not to insult the Jewish students.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The rise of Nazism in Germany was very-- the Jewish people [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] knew that they were dangerous.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They expected danger.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not too familiar with Nazism.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They knew the Germans from World War I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But some of them ignored them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We, the young people, of course, we couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were aware that we were fighting Nazism and ideas from Nazism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The problem was it's--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had demonstrations--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Against Nazism, against anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because those days, the Polish people-- one wing, the nationalists, [POLISH], they adopted many things from Nazis, from the German Nazis.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the anti-Semitism became unbearable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even that time, the Prime Minister, Skladkowski, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he didn't allow pogroms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't allow beating of Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But fighting economically, he said, [SPEAKING POLISH], this you can do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, well, that time in our city, in all, all the-- all the cities, you know, anti-Semitism became rampant.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't buy from a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Don't support the Jewish business system.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Don't-- just buy from Polish merchants.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This, this-- it, it did not affect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, you see, how did it affect my father, you're asking me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once-- he had a taxi that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- it wasn't like here, that, that every taxi had to, to go through a, a, a once a year.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Over there, they came, all of a sudden, to the marketplace, where my father was, and the other taxis.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They checked all the taxis that there were over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They left all go, but my father's taxi--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the government, special agents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took off the license plates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we couldn't-- we couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after a while, we had to go through.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
